name: Tezzy Everydays #11 | Cousin Itt | May 17th, 2021
description: This is the 11th day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos. I loooooove the Addams Family pinball machine. When the Thing hand came out of the box and picked up the ball for the first time, I lost my mind. By far, Cousin Itt is the most iconic character on the classic TV show I enjoyed so much as a child watching reruns in the 80's. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
